name: ASDF-Symphony
description:
A game made in 2 hours for a Game Jam with the theme "Don't stop". 

ASDF-Symphony is reminiscent of many rhythm game you probably have played in the past - Press the keys at the right time! 

contrary to other rhythm games, this game doesn't have sound or music though, due to the time constraints the jam imposed (it should have been a 30 minute jam, but I overshot with my time).
